{"data":[{"id":564146117,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":307595822,"title":"高中生对哥德巴赫猜想的证明有哪些错误？","question_type":"normal","created":1546272354,"updated_time":1546301579,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/307595822","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"4b85011e25a8d4a13e26d13cb0043947","url_token":"","name":"知乎用户","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":18,"is_followed":false,"is_privacy":true},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/564146117","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546334992,"updated_time":1546335059,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":0,"comment_count":0,"is_sticky":false,"admin_closed_comment":false,"comment_permission":"all","can_comment":{"reason":"","status":true},"reshipment_settings":"allowed","content":"\u003cp\u003e1）准备中有\u003c/p\u003e\u003cblockquote\u003e设集合 A 为所有满足两个质数之和的偶数的集合。且此时质数包括正质数和负质数；\u003cbr\u003e但之后证明说明负质数没有定义好的，那么A也是没有定义好的，怎么可以随便用呢？\u003c/blockquote\u003e\u003cp\u003e可能作者想定义所有的偶数集合\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e与大于2的偶数集合。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cblockquote\u003e2）\u003cbr\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=%5Cbecause2%3D%28-1%29%2B3\" alt=\"\\because2=(-1)+3\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e，\u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=%5Ctherefore\" alt=\"\\therefore\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e得到一个新的猜想，即\u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=%5Cforall%7Bn%7D%5Cin%5Cmathbb%7BN%7D_%2B%2C2n%5Cin%7BB%7D\" alt=\"\\forall{n}\\in\\mathbb{N}_+,2n\\in{B}\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e或\u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=2n%3D%28-1%29%2B%282n%2B1%29%2C2n%2B1%5Cin%5Cmathbb%7BP%7D\" alt=\"2n=(-1)+(2n+1),2n+1\\in\\mathbb{P}\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e，将其称为哥德巴赫猜想变式一。\u003c/blockquote\u003e\u003cp\u003e这里的因为所以写得很奇怪（实际上我觉得不可以这样写）。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e但我可以勉强理解，作者想提出一个“弱的”哥德巴赫猜想。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e这里有一个明显的错误（或者说奇怪的地方），\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e因为作者设集合 \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=B\" alt=\"B\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e 为所有满足两个质数之和的偶数的集合。且此时质数只包括正质数；\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e所以或前面的论断（即\u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=%5Cforall%7Bn%7D%5Cin%5Cmathbb%7BN%7D_%2B%2C2n%5Cin%7BB%7D\" alt=\"\\forall{n}\\in\\mathbb{N}_+,2n\\in{B}\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e或）显然是错的。（2显然不属于B）\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e而或后面的论断显然是对的。所以作者提出了一个trivial 的论断。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e3）看不下去了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e这个可能是个钓鱼问题吧。新年快乐！\u003c/p\u003e","editable_content":"","excerpt":"1）准备中有设集合 A 为所有满足两个质数之和的偶数的集合。且此时质数包括正质数和负质数； 但之后证明说明负质数没有定义好的，那么A也是没有定义好的，怎么可以随便用呢？可能作者想定义所有的偶数集合与大于2的偶数集合。2） \\because2=(-1)+3，\\theref…","collapsed_by":"nobody","collapse_reason":"","annotation_action":[],"mark_infos":[],"relevant_info":{"is_relevant":false,"relevant_type":"","relevant_text":""},"suggest_edit":{"reason":"","status":false,"tip":"","title":"","unnormal_details":{"status":"","description":"","reason":"","reason_id":0,"note":""},"url":""},"is_labeled":false,"reward_info":{"can_open_reward":false,"is_rewardable":false,"reward_member_count":0,"reward_total_money":0,"tagline":""},"relationship":{"is_author":false,"is_authorized":false,"is_nothelp":false,"is_thanked":false,"voting":0,"upvoted_followees":[]}}],"paging":{"is_end":false,"is_start":false,"next":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/307595822/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomment_count%2Ccan_comment%2Ccontent%2Ceditable_content%2Cvoteup_count%2Creshipment_settings%2Ccomment_permission%2Ccreated_time%2Cupdated_time%2Creview_info%2Crelevant_info%2Cquestion%2Cexcerpt%2Crelationship.is_authorized%2Ci